WHAT THIS COVERS
----------------
This licence applies to the community's own contribution to this repository, namely: the
compilation and selection of the data, its structure and schema, its identifiers and normalisation,
the corrections and verification contributed by the community, and the accompanying documentation
and tooling.

It does NOT grant, and cannot grant, any rights in third-party intellectual property that the data
refers to. See NOTICE for the full intellectual-property position. Nothing here is a licence to any
Games Workshop Limited property.


IN SHORT
--------
You are free to share and adapt this dataset, including commercially, provided that:

  ATTRIBUTION  — you credit "the IRONBUILT community dataset" and link back to this repository,
                 and you do not remove the contribution log or the contributors' credits; and

  SHARE-ALIKE  — if you remix, transform or build upon it, you distribute your version under this
                 same licence, so the community's work stays available to the community.

  NO ENDORSEMENT — you may not imply that IRONBUILT, IRONBUILT LLC, or any contributor endorses you
                 or your use.

Attribution is owed to the community, not to any single maintainer: this dataset exists because
players report and correct it. See contributions/CONTRIBUTIONS.md for the record of who contributed
what.


NOTE FOR MAINTAINERS
--------------------
This file is a proposal pending review and is not legal advice. The licence choice has real
consequences (share-alike is deliberately "sticky" and constrains closed-source reuse, including
possibly your own). Have it reviewed by a qualified IP lawyer before relying on it, and remove this
note once it is confirmed.
